SOM firmware is the firmware which runs on the EIC7X SoC of the SOM board.
The firmware includes ddr_init.bin,sys_init.bin and bootloader.bin.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.ddr_init.bin: DDR trainning and initialization firmware.
  For 16GB DDR, the firmware is ddr16G_init.bin.
  For 32GB DDR, the firmware is ddr32G_init.bin.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.sys_init.bin: Board initialization, like PLL initialization and fan startup.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3.bootloader.bin: It consists of OpenSBI and U-boot.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Notes:
nsign_bootloader_secboot_ddr_16G_dvb2.bin is the bootchain file gengerated by
the nsign tool after packing ddr16G_init.bin, sys_init.bin and bootloader.bin.

nsign_bootloader_secboot_ddr_32G_dvb2.bin is the bootchain file gengerated by
the nsign tool after packing ddr32G_init.bin, sys_init.bin and bootloader.bin.

Users can generate your own bootchain with ddr_init.bin, sys_init.bin and
your own bootloader.bin by the nsign tool.
